item.title: CVE-2023-45192|2024-06-06T18:49:05.734Z -- ibm -- engineering%20requirements%20management%20doors%20next
item.description: IBM Engineering Requirements Management DOORS Next 7.0.2 and 7.0.3 is vulnerable to an XML External Entity Injection (XXE) attack when processing XML data. A remote attacker could exploit this vulnerability to expose sensitive information or consume memory resources. IBM X-Force ID: 268758.
